      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute beauty. It's in pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one for you. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
