    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2005 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-quality condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precision-gated 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanically pristine, the VANOS system has been overhauled, rod bearings replaced, and the rear subframe reinforced with a structural plate kit for total chassis rigidity. The factory limited-slip differential provides exceptional corner-exit traction, complemented by an untouched OEM suspension geometry. Paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior retains its factory matte finish with zero bolster wear. A turn-key mechanical masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
