    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously garaged and climate-controlled since day one, preserving the deep, mirror-like finish of its original factory paint with absolutely zero swirl marks, dings, or stone chips. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of creasing or bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since purchase. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium infotainment suite, operates with factory precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, featuring a complete, top-tier service history and exceptionally low mileage. The engine bay is immaculate, and the tires are high-performance replacements with less than 500 miles on them. Recently treated with a professional-grade ceramic coating, this car represents the absolute pinnacle of its model year. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a 'time capsule' vehicle in flawless condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
